Interface GenericEntry

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, Consumer<NetworkTableValue>, GenericPublisher, GenericSubscriber, Publisher, PubSub, Subscriber, Supplier<NetworkTableValue>
public interface GenericEntry extends GenericSubscriber, GenericPublisher
NetworkTables generic entry.

Unlike NetworkTableEntry, the entry goes away when close() is called.
